# Chiefs Narrative engine — environment.
# Copy to `.env` for local runs (the run scripts auto-load it). ALL are optional:
# with none set, the deterministic offline writer produces a complete edition.

# --- Force a specific writer (optional) ---
# One of: grok | openai | anthropic | claude-cli | codex-cli | offline
# Leave unset to auto-detect: Grok -> OpenAI -> Anthropic -> claude CLI ->
# codex CLI -> offline.
# CHIEFS_PROVIDER=

# --- Grok / xAI (takes precedence over OpenAI when set) ---
# Either variable name works.
# XAI_API_KEY=xai-...
# GROK_API_KEY=xai-...
# GROK_MODEL=grok-4
# XAI_BASE_URL=https://api.x.ai/v1

# --- OpenAI ---
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
# OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o
# OPENAI_BASE_URL=https://api.openai.com/v1

# --- Anthropic ---
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-sonnet-5

# --- Optional sportsbook consensus (The Odds API) ---
# Without it we still use ESPN's DraftKings line + FPI projection + Polymarket.
# ODDS_API_KEY=
